{"tid":714163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"咁重口味？馬浚偉想問麥玲玲攞裸照","createTime":"2018-06-23T12:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T13:16:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d238210aca68b09f2d414018b19d3c60703ce9bf","tid":714163,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"藝人馬浚偉出席太陽計劃活動，笑言現時朋友whatsapp他只有兩個目標，第一是訂舞台劇飛，第二是想知《宮心計2深宮計》劇透，但他表示不會爆響口：「劇透咗就唔好睇，依家都好快就大結局，跟住落嚟嘅劇情係會幾驚喜，都好開心呢套劇喺香港同內地有咁大回響。」講到因公司問題未能為此劇宣傳的周秀娜謂很想被「召入宮」，問到他們一班演員可會約出來？他表示：「隨時，不過我呢排冇時間，可能會叫佢嚟睇我嘅舞台劇，其實之後我都冇時間宣傳《宮》，至於公司嘅嘢我理唔到咁多。」但他大讚周秀娜演出好：「其實拍劇嗰陣佢同時拍緊戲，但一埋位時就好精神，好專業，佢冇乜點拍過古裝，所以做足功課、背好對白，有唔識又謙虛問人。」<br />\n<br />\n拍搞笑版後傳 <br />\n馬浚偉亦謂《宮》現時內地點擊率有22億，如果之後達30億就會大晒與胡定欣的「床照」，過了30億之後就暫時未想到，但笑言可以玩直播。問他可是直播除衫？他靈機一觸笑言：「網上有人key咗麥玲玲個樣喺周秀娜身度，麥玲玲又真係幾似唐代美人，或者叫佢攞張裸照出嚟。其實麥玲玲又幾襯古裝，可以開套後傳，叫做《唐玄宗與唐貴妃》，搵我同麥玲玲嚟做，拍個搞笑版。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/204551_df45bd5d1081fd3687f94d737758e06c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F204551_df45bd5d1081fd3687f94d737758e06c.png&h=781b56c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180623/mobile/bkn-20180623170444450-0623_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180623%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180623170444450-0623_00862_001.html&d=FiAKgoml5Zz3hpx%2Bxsr10ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b3adf1a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180623/mobile/bkn-20180623170444450-0623_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"683fce441a7575ab3802ab109f32ffd2e81750d9","tid":714163,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:47:00.000Z","msg":"馬撚真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f5029462de3638a626192b8523f89426aefe36","tid":714163,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"麥00咁大波 睇下都無妨"},{"pid":"45bf2d75acbd60b57c3ad96a625ab5623ea50424","tid":714163,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"契到麥玲玲就發達"},{"pid":"acf279ba0209ed41d2230741f8e95c5cb1724ee5","tid":714163,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"mc00都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c145d31e2a6c550b2cfa281c489f37dfde9139","tid":714163,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"夾腸應該幾正"},{"pid":"94976db0c4403c82f737951c777bd86a6e42a2af","tid":714163,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/deb/7b4/deb7b4e21071ed9e98e0283aa9f6a7a8b56a6168_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fdeb%2F7b4%2Fdeb7b4e21071ed9e98e0283aa9f6a7a8b56a6168_b.jpg&h=3d1a0fe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2015648f2744ab38ec74c9dba21d3496874596ba","tid":714163,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"勿00係咪落左桃花降去馬撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}